## Data Protection
- Never store sensitive data in AsyncStorage without encryption
- Use SecureStore for sensitive information
- Implement proper session/token management
- Sanitize all user inputs before processing

## Authentication
- Implement proper authentication flows with secure tokens
- Use biometric authentication when available
- Follow OAuth 2.0 best practices for social auth
- Implement proper session timeout handling

## Network Security
- Use HTTPS for all network requests
- Implement certificate pinning for critical operations
- Add proper request/response validation
- Log security-related events appropriately
